%vlocity_namespace%__InternalNotes__c: This formula is addedd or SIC code for the condition so that User should still be allowed to proceed with quoting Medical, Dental and Vision (given Medical, Dental or Vision was selected on Category Selection screen)

%vlocity_namespace%__PropertySet__c.expression: IF(%MinInfo:TypeAheadSIC-Block:LDPlan% == "life", 'This industry is not eligible for Short Term Disability coverage', IF(%MinInfo:TypeAheadSIC-Block:LDPlan% == "STD", 'This industry is not eligible for Life coverage', IF(%CategorySelection:LAndDPlanType%, IF(OR(%CategorySelection:MedicalPlanType%,%CategorySelection:DentalPlanType%,%CategorySelection:VisionPlanType%), "LD&OtherSelected", IF(%MinInfo:TypeAheadSIC-Block:LDPlan%=="life,STD", "NA", "NotSelected")), "Nothing")))

Name: SIC_life_STD_Formula
